\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>价格低廉 拥有最好的性价比。</p>\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>小型轻便 世界最小的体积和最轻的重量：235g（不含电池）</p>\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>简单迅速 &ldquo;拭取后检测&rdquo;，就是如此简单，10秒即可得到结果。</p>\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>超高敏感 同时检测ATP及AMP（日本专利号No.3409962）</p>\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>不仅能检测ATP(腺苷三磷酸)，还能检测AMP(腺苷磷酸)，更脏的也能检测。</p>\r\n<p class=\"t\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体; text-indent: 0em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; color: red;\">&bull;&nbsp;</span>适用于生产现场的清洁度管理和厨房的清洁度管理&middot;卫生教育。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p class=\"b\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 18px; letter-spacing: 1px; font-weight: bold; font-family: Arial, Helvetica, 宋体;\